------------------------------------

1.) Overview

csketchp is a basic tool for calculating Riemann sums of curve sketches.

It is intended to be an educational aid.

------------------------------------

2.) Compiling

Make sure SFML 1.6 is properly installed and configured.

On Debian 7.0, the following packages are required:
libsfml-graphics1.6
libsfml-window1.6
libsfml-system1.6
libsfml-dev

To compile, issue the following console commands in the parent directory:

cmake .
make

Program options can be found in /bin/options.cfg, and adjusted to suit the user.

------------------------------------
